{"acceptance_criteria":"","actor":"","agent_state":"","assignee":null,"await_id":"","await_type":"","close_reason":"Converted options/popup to vanilla DOM. Note: 4 Firefox warnings remain due to Plasmo's React requirement - would need to abandon Plasmo or suppress warnings to fully eliminate.","closed_at":"2026-03-03T00:42:23Z","closed_by_session":"","compacted_at":null,"compacted_at_commit":null,"compaction_level":0,"content_hash":"f85c9bd846f8c6365c3057303fe8e1fc222aaaf429f6541db51346d6fbb251a0","created_at":"2026-03-02T23:59:31Z","created_by":"Mike Crowe","crystallizes":0,"defer_until":null,"description":"## Overview\n\nRemove React dependency from Options page and Popup to eliminate the remaining 4 Firefox extension warnings (UNSAFE_VAR_ASSIGNMENT from React's innerHTML usage).\n\n## Current State\n\n- **9 warnings** originally → **4 warnings** remaining after partial fixes\n- React is used in:\n  - `src/options/` (10 files) - Settings UI with 13 checkboxes + tab switching\n  - `src/popup.tsx` - Domain bias display with async fetch\n\n## Remaining Warnings\n\nAll 4 are `UNSAFE_VAR_ASSIGNMENT` from React's internal `innerHTML` handling for SVG elements.\n\n## Conversion Plan\n\n### Phase 1: Convert Options Page (~1 hour)\n\n1. **Static components** (easy):\n   - `intro.tsx` → static HTML\n   - `release-notes.tsx` → static HTML\n\n2. **Interactive components**:\n   - `options.tsx` - Replace checkbox callbacks with event listeners\n   - `tab-groups.tsx` - Replace 13 `useStorage` hooks with `chrome.storage.local` API\n   - `tabs.tsx` - Replace tab state with storage API\n   - `tab.tsx` - Convert to vanilla click handlers\n   - `tab-contents.tsx` - Simple show/hide logic\n\n### Phase 2: Convert Popup (~30 min)\n\n- `popup.tsx` - Replace `useState`/`useEffect` with:\n  - Direct `chrome.storage` calls\n  - Async/await for background messaging\n  - DOM manipulation for updates\n\n### Phase 3: Cleanup\n\n- Remove React/react-dom from dependencies\n- Remove unused React-related type definitions\n- Update Plasmo config if needed\n- Verify build size reduction\n- Run Firefox linter to confirm 0 warnings\n\n## Technical Approach\n\nReplace Plasmo's `useStorage` hook pattern:\n\n```typescript\n// Before (React)\nconst [value, setValue] = useStorage(\"key\", false)\n\n// After (Vanilla)\nconst value = await chrome.storage.local.get(\"key\")\nawait chrome.storage.local.set({ key: newValue })\nchrome.storage.onChanged.addListener((changes) =\u003e { ... })\n```\n\n## Benefits\n\n- Eliminate all 4 remaining Firefox warnings\n- Reduce bundle size (remove React runtime)\n- Simpler codebase with fewer dependencies\n- Faster extension load times\n\n## Estimated Effort\n\n- **Total: ~1.5-2 hours**\n- Options: ~1 hour\n- Popup: ~30 min\n- Cleanup/testing: ~30 min","design":"","due_at":null,"ephemeral":0,"estimated_minutes":null,"event_kind":"","external_ref":null,"hook_bead":"","id":"smb-wq3","is_template":0,"issue_type":"epic","last_activity":null,"metadata":"{}","mol_type":"","notes":"","original_size":null,"owner":"drmikecrowe@gmail.com","payload":"","pinned":0,"priority":1,"quality_score":null,"rig":"","role_bead":"","role_type":"","sender":"","source_repo":"","source_system":"","spec_id":"","status":"closed","target":"","timeout_ns":0,"title":"Remove React from Options and Popup to eliminate Firefox warnings","updated_at":"2026-03-03T00:42:23Z","waiters":"","wisp_type":"","work_type":""}
